---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';

const faqs = [
  {
    question: "Do you visit clients on-site in Kannur?",
    answer: "Yes. For Kannur-based clients, we regularly meet in person at your office or ours at TK Junction, Thana. On-site sessions are especially useful during discovery, training, and major launches. For clients elsewhere in Kerala or India, we work over Google Meet, WhatsApp, and Slack with the same level of responsiveness.",
  },
  {
    question: "Can you support Malayalam-speaking founders and teams?",
    answer: "All four co-founders are from Kerala and speak Malayalam, English, and Hindi. We translate technical concepts into plain language so non-technical owners stay in control of their software decisions. Documentation, contracts, and final deliverables are typically in English for portability, but day-to-day communication happens in whichever language is comfortable.",
  },
  {
    question: "What's a typical project timeline for a Kerala SMB?",
    answer: "A focused internal tool or website ships in 4 to 8 weeks. Custom platforms with integrations and admin panels take 8 to 16 weeks. Full SaaS products with multi-tenancy and billing take 3 to 6 months. We give you a milestone-based plan during the first scoping call.",
  },
  {
    question: "How does pricing compare to outsourcing to Bangalore or offshore?",
    answer: "Per-hour rates from Kannur tend to be 30–50% lower than tier-1 Bangalore agencies and far lower than US/EU outsourcing, while quality matches or exceeds because we run our own SaaS products in production. You also avoid travel, time-zone friction, and the layers of project managers that big-city agencies add to the bill.",
  },
  {
    question: "Do you work with clients outside Kerala?",
    answer: "Yes. Our portfolio includes clients in the UAE, across India, and remote SaaS subscribers globally. The Kannur office is our base; the work goes wherever the client is.",
  },
];
---

<Layout
  title="Software Development Company in Kannur, Kerala"
  description="Kannur-based software development company building custom software, SaaS platforms, web apps, and mobile apps for businesses across Kerala, India, and the Gulf. Visit our office at TK Junction, Thana."
  keywords="software development company in Kannur, software company Kannur, custom software Kerala, web development Kannur, mobile app development Kannur, SaaS Kerala, software developers Kannur, IT company Kannur, software agency Kerala"
  service={{
    name: "Software Development Company in Kannur",
    description: "Local software development company offering custom software, SaaS platforms, web apps, and mobile apps for businesses in Kannur, Kerala, and across India.",
    serviceType: "Software Development",
  }}
  faqs={faqs}
>
  <Navbar />

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero__glow"></div>
    <div class="page-hero__bg-dots"></div>
    <div class="container page-hero__inner">
      <div class="badge badge-sky">Kannur · Kerala · India</div>
      <h1 class="page-hero__title">
        Software Development Company in <span class="text-gradient">Kannur, Kerala</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="page-hero__desc">
        Four engineers from Thalassery Engineering College who came home to build software the way it should be built: close to the client, properly scoped, and shipped to last. Our office is at TK Junction, Thana, Kannur. Our work spans Kerala, India, and the Gulf.
      </p>
      <div class="page-hero__cta">
        <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Talk to Our Team</a>
        <a href="https://wa.me/919645091256?text=Hi%20N3%20Global%20Tech%2C%20I%27d%20like%20to%20discuss%20a%20project." target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-ghost btn-lg">WhatsApp Us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section content-section">
    <div class="container content-narrow">

      <h2>Why a Kannur-based partner makes a difference</h2>
      <p>
        Most Kerala businesses end up with one of two bad options when they need software: a generic SaaS tool that almost fits, or an agency in Bangalore or Mumbai that bills in 15-minute increments and treats your project as one of fifty. We sit in between. We are local enough to drive to your site for a discovery session, technical enough to ship platforms that hold up under real production load, and structured enough that your project doesn't drift.
      </p>
      <p>
        For founders in Kerala, this matters in three specific ways. First, communication: we work in Malayalam, English, and Hindi, so technical decisions don't get lost in translation. Second, accountability: when something breaks, you can call the person who built it, and that person is in the same time zone. Third, alignment with how Kerala businesses actually run, which is rarely the same as the assumptions baked into off-the-shelf American software.
      </p>

      <h2>Who we work with locally</h2>
      <p>
        Our Kerala client base spans several real categories. We've built and continue to maintain platforms for:
      </p>
      <ul class="content-list">
        <li><strong>Auto service centres</strong> running on <a href="/products/">N3 ServiceBook</a>, replacing paper job cards with a clean platform for booking, invoicing, and customer follow-ups.</li>
        <li><strong>Gyms and fitness studios</strong> using N3 FitBook for memberships, attendance, trainer schedules, and recurring payments.</li>
        <li><strong>Wooden-flooring and home brands</strong> like Viera, with an immersive 3D website paired with a custom CRM for site staff and operations.</li>
        <li><strong>Aviation services</strong> like Flyger, where we built a professional global-facing site for a flight operations provider headquartered partly in the region.</li>
        <li><strong>Training institutes, retail stores, and consultancies</strong> needing internal dashboards, customer portals, or end-to-end automations of paperwork-heavy processes.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        Some of our clients are in Kannur and Thalassery. Others are in Kochi, Wayanad, Calicut, and across the state. We also support clients in the UAE and remote subscribers globally on our own SaaS products.
      </p>

      <h2>What we build</h2>
      <p>
        Our work falls into four overlapping areas. Each links to a more detailed page if you want the technical depth.
      </p>
      <ul class="content-list">
        <li><a href="/custom-software-development/"><strong>Custom software development</strong></a> for businesses that have outgrown spreadsheets and off-the-shelf tools. Web apps, mobile apps, internal dashboards, and automations.</li>
        <li><a href="/saas-development-company/"><strong>SaaS platforms</strong></a> with multi-tenant architecture, subscription billing, and the cloud infrastructure to scale to thousands of users.</li>
        <li><strong>Web development</strong>: marketing sites, e-commerce, portals, and complex landing pages built with React, Next.js, Astro, and Node.js.</li>
        <li><strong>Mobile app development</strong>: native iOS and Android, plus React Native and Flutter for cross-platform builds.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        See the full list on our <a href="/services/">services page</a> or browse <a href="/work/">recent client projects</a>.
      </p>

      <h2>Visit our Kannur office</h2>
      <p>
        We're easy to find. Our office is at TK Junction, near Capital Mall, in Thana, Kannur. Central, well-connected, and walkable from most of the town. Drop in for a coffee and a project conversation, or schedule a video call if you're elsewhere.
      </p>
      <address class="local-nap">
        <strong>N3 Global Tech</strong><br />
        TK Junction, Near Capital Mall,<br />
        Thana, Kannur, Kerala 670002, India<br />
        <a href="tel:+919645091256">+91 96450 91256</a> ·
        <a href="https://wa.me/919645091256?text=Hi%20N3%20Global%20Tech%2C%20I%27d%20like%20to%20discuss%20a%20project." target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">WhatsApp</a> ·
        <a href="mailto:contact@n3global.tech">contact@n3global.tech</a>
      </address>

      <div class="map-wrap">
        <iframe
          src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3902.0!2d75.3704!3d11.8745!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0x0!2sTK%20Junction%2C%20Thana%2C%20Kannur%2C%20Kerala%20670002!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1700000000000"
          width="100%"
          height="320"
          style="border:0; border-radius: 1rem;"
          allowfullscreen=""
          loading="lazy"
          referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
          title="N3 Global Tech office on Google Maps"
        ></iframe>
      </div>

      <h2>Frequently asked questions</h2>
      {faqs.map(f => (
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>{f.question}</h3>
          <p>{f.answer}</p>
        </div>
      ))}

      <div class="page-cta">
        <h2>Ready to start your project?</h2>
        <p>Call, WhatsApp, email, or fill out the form. You'll hear back within 24 hours, with the founder who'll work on your project on the call.</p>
        <div class="page-cta__actions">
          <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-primary btn-xl">Start a Project</a>
          <a href="https://wa.me/919645091256?text=Hi%20N3%20Global%20Tech%2C%20I%27d%20like%20to%20discuss%20a%20project." target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-ghost btn-xl" style="background:rgba(37,211,102,0.95); color:#fff; border-color:rgba(37,211,102,0.95);">Chat on WhatsApp</a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    position: relative;
    padding: calc(80px + 4rem) 0 4rem;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f8fafc 0%, #ffffff 100%);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .page-hero__glow {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 800px; height: 400px;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(14,165,233,0.18) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .page-hero__bg-dots {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image: radial-gradient(circle, var(--sky-200) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 36px 36px;
    opacity: 0.2;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .page-hero__inner {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 820px;
  }
  .page-hero__title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.25rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin: 1rem 0 1.25rem;
  }
  .page-hero__desc {
    font-size: 1.08rem;
    color: var(--gray-600);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .page-hero__cta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .btn-lg { padding: 0.85rem 2rem; font-size: 1rem; }
  .btn-xl { padding: 1rem 2.5rem; font-size: 1.05rem; }

  .content-section { padding: 4rem 0 6rem; }
  .content-narrow { max-width: 880px; }
  .content-narrow h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    margin: 3rem 0 1rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .content-narrow h2:first-child { margin-top: 0; }
  .content-narrow h3 {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 1.75rem 0 0.55rem;
    color: var(--gray-900);
  }
  .content-narrow p {
    color: var(--gray-700);
    line-height: 1.85;
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    font-size: 1.02rem;
  }
  .content-narrow a {
    color: var(--sky-700);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }
  .content-list {
    margin: 1rem 0 1.5rem 1.5rem;
    color: var(--gray-700);
    line-height: 1.85;
  }
  .content-list li { margin-bottom: 0.85rem; }

  .local-nap {
    background: var(--sky-50);
    padding: 1.5rem 1.75rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--gray-700);
    font-style: normal;
    margin: 1.5rem 0 2rem;
  }
  .local-nap strong { color: var(--gray-900); }

  .map-wrap {
    border-radius: 1rem;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }
  .map-wrap iframe { display: block; }

  .faq-item {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
    padding: 1.5rem 0;
  }
  .faq-item h3 {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
  }
  .faq-item p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--gray-600);
  }

  .page-cta {
    margin-top: 4rem;
    padding: 3rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gray-900), var(--sky-900));
    color: #fff;
    border-radius: 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .page-cta h2 {
    color: #fff;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
  }
  .page-cta p {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.78);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    max-width: 540px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }
  .page-cta__actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
</style>
